## Import


An existing resource can be imported using its type token, name, and identifier, e.g.

```sh
$ pulumi import azure-native:storsimple:FileServer HSDK-4XY4FI2IVG /subscriptions/9eb689cd-7243-43b4-b6f6-5c65cb296641/resourceGroups/ResourceGroupForSDKTest/providers/Microsoft.StorSimple/managers/hAzureSDKOperations/devices/hsdk-4xy4fi2ivg/fileServers/HSDK-4XY4FI2IVG 
```
